{{Infobox government agency|name=視聽媒體委員會|seal=|logo=General Commission for Audiovisual Media logo.svg|formed=2012年|jurisdiction={{沙特阿拉伯}}|headquarters={{flagicon|沙特阿拉伯}}利雅得|employees=|budget=|parent_department=[[媒体部_(沙特阿拉伯)|媒体部]]|website=https://www.gcam.gov.sa/}}'''視聽媒體委員會（GCAM；'''{{Lang-ar|الهيئة العامة للإعلام المرئي والمسموع|al-Hy'eh al'Amah lel-E'elam al-Mar'ey wal-Masmoo'}} ）是[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯的]]政府组织，于2012年成立，负责对沙特阿拉伯境内视听媒体传输及内容开发进行监管。 <ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Authority to monitor audiovisual media|url=http://www.arabnews.com/saudi-arabia/authority-monitor-audiovisual-media|accessdate=2019-03-19|date=2012-09-04|work=Arab News|language=en|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223191857/http://www.arabnews.com/saudi-arabia/authority-monitor-audiovisual-media|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=General Commission of Audiovisual Media -- GCAM|url=https://www.linkedin.com/company/general-commission-of-audiovisual-media|date=19 March 2019|work=Linkedin}}</ref> GCAM虽然是[[媒体部（沙特阿拉伯）|媒体部]]下辖机构，但此机构的财务和行政管理不受干涉。   此机构现任首席执行官是Esra Assery。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Who's Who: Esra Assery, CEO of the General Commission for Audiovisual Media|url=https://arab.news/pcm8j|accessdate=2021-02-14|date=2021-02-11|work=Arab News|language=en}}</ref>

== 职务范围 ==
GCAM根据沙特的“媒体法规”对视听内容进行监管，并提供相关服务以管理相关内容的宣传。 <ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=New Saudi authority for the regulation of Audio and Visual Media|url=https://www.tamimi.com/law-update-articles/new-saudi-authority-for-the-regulation-of-audio-and-visual-media/|accessdate=2019-03-19|work=Al Tamimi & Company|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128142358/https://www.tamimi.com/law-update-articles/new-saudi-authority-for-the-regulation-of-audio-and-visual-media/|dead-url=no}}</ref>亦对视听媒体传输和内容的许可证进行发行和管理。  <ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Authority to monitor audiovisual media|url=http://www.arabnews.com/saudi-arabia/authority-monitor-audiovisual-media|accessdate=2019-03-19|date=2012-09-04|work=Arab News|language=en}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[http://www.arabnews.com/saudi-arabia/authority-monitor-audiovisual-media "Authority to monitor audiovisual media"]. ''Arab News''. 2012-09-04<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2019-03-19</span></span>.</cite></ref> GCAM还负责处理并制定与媒体有关的技术问题和规范，例如为批准企业或个人使用频谱或媒体传输设备。 

== 沙特电影 ==
2018年12月，由文化和信息部（现为[[媒体部（沙特阿拉伯）|媒体部]]）主持的视听媒体委员会下令恢复全沙特阿拉伯电影院的运营，该委员会将负责向电影院颁发营业许可。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Cinemas to re-open in Saudi Arabia as of 2018, Ministry of Information confirms|url=http://www.arabnews.com/node/1207261/saudi-arabia|accessdate=2019-03-19|date=2017-12-11|work=Arab News|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033857/https://www.arabnews.com/node/1207261/saudi-arabia|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Saudi Arabia Lifts Ban On Movie Theatres At Last|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/dominicdudley/2017/12/11/saudi-lifts-ban-on-cinemas/|accessdate=2019-03-19|author=Dudley|first=Dominic|work=Forbes|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126224431/https://www.forbes.com/sites/dominicdudley/2017/12/11/saudi-lifts-ban-on-cinemas/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

